# Design System — Evidencija zaposlenih

## Typeface

- Primary: system-ui stack (Apple-like):
  ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Display", "SF Pro Text", "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji"
- Use font-smoothing where possible.

## Theme

- Default: Light, high contrast, “Apple-like” clean surfaces
- Emphasis on subtle borders + soft shadows + restrained accent usage

## Color tokens (semantic)

- bg: app background
- surface: cards/panels/modals
- surface2: elevated surface/hover
- border: subtle separators
- text: primary text
- muted: secondary text
- accent: primary action / highlights
- accent2: secondary accent (rare)
- danger: destructive actions
- success/warn: status indications (use sparingly)

## Layout & spacing

- Use consistent spacing scale (Tailwind default)
- Containers: max width ~ 1100–1200px, centered, generous padding
- Cards: 16px–20px padding, radius 16px, subtle border

## Components

- Buttons:
  - Primary: accent bg, white text
  - Secondary: surface bg + border
  - Destructive: danger
  - States: hover, active, disabled, focus ring
- Inputs:
  - Surface bg, border, focus ring (accent)
  - Clear error state (danger border + helper text)
- Modals:
  - Surface panel, shadow, backdrop blur if available
- Tables/lists:
  - Row hover, subtle dividers

## Interaction

- No animation-heavy UI. Use subtle transitions only (150–200ms).
